name: Serie Signaturas Dueto Robusto
additionalNotes:
Royal Agio Cigars has announced the latest line for the Balmoral: Serie Signaturas, a focus on collaboration.

The first cigar of the new line will aptly be called Dueto, made by Ernesto Perez-Carrillo Jr.’s Tabacalera La Alianza S.A. factory. The blend uses a Nicaraguan wrapper from Jalapa, a binder from Estelí, Nicaragua and a mixture of Nicaragua and Agio’s signature Brazilian mata norte fillers.
